snippet.textDisplay:
So my school isn't completely shut down but no one goes anymore. But our school had closed early this term so they can get online school ready for next term. Australians will under stand the term thingy. We just don't have 3 months holiday we have it all separated.

Anyway. My mum is also working form home cause she doesn't need to be at work as she works in an office. My dad still goes to work because he builds house frames and kinda can't really do that at our home.

Anyway. Our mum didn't want us being bored just doing work so we made a roster. We do art, baking, sewing and fitness all on different days for an hour. And we only do 4 days a week so on Friday we can do whatever we want.
Anyway. On Monday we did art for the first time. And I tried doing abstract art following a torurial. It looks like really awful. My mum is lying to me and saying it looks good. But it really doesn't. And she tells me she's never lie to me. Haha lol. But I did a drawing on my laptop and it doesn't look too bad. It's just the night sky, and a realistic moon. Like it looks real. The moon look real not anything else. So I'm gonna try paint that when we do art again.
It will probs end up awful again.
